--[[ test
    ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ║            ScriptCapture — Injection Detector               ║
    ║  Detects scripts injected AFTER the game finishes loading.  ║
    ║  Ignores all scripts already present on the client.         ║
    ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

    HOW IT WORKS:
      1. Waits for the game to fully load (ContentProvider + replication).
      2. Takes a snapshot of every script instance already in the game tree.
      3. From that point on, ONLY scripts that are NEW (not in the snapshot)
         will be captured — i.e. scripts injected by a third-party executor
         or remote injection after load time.
      4. Captures name, class, full path, properties, source (if accessible),
         and the exact timestamp of injection.

    PLACE THIS IN: StarterPlayerScripts  (or execute via an executor)
--]]

